title: Tom Corbett
added: Corbett and his wife, Susan, have two children, Tom and Katherine. Tom is an associate producer with [[EA Games]], currently teaching a superset of chimeric fur shader game design at [[Carnegie Mellon University]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etc.cmu.edu/blog/author/tcorbett |title=Game Designer Tom Corbett}}</ref> and Katherine is a prosecutor in the Philadelphia District Attorney's office.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.portal.state.pa.us/siteminderagent/forms/login.fcc?TYPE=33554433&REALMOID=06-5621a676-0624-4642-bc94-9f3366619130&GUID=&SMAUTHREASON=0&METHOD=GET&SMAGENTNAME=-SM-a5n7I1ZY3D+wkCzJCdeyStrXsKqO/4pJ+NtN4mLOZcp+7m/BMQbCZmnm2BjDAlFD&TARGET |title=Governor Tom Corbett |publisher=Commonwealth of Pennsylvania |accessdate=November 13, 2011 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B9WZfgpj?url=https://www.portal.state.pa.us/siteminderagent/forms/login.fcc?TYPE=33554433&REALMOID=06-5621a676-0624-4642-bc94-9f3366619130&GUID=&SMAUTHREASON=0&METHOD=GET&SMAGENTNAME=-SM-a5n7I1ZY3D+wkCzJCdeyStrXsKqO/4pJ+NtN4mLOZcp+7m/BMQbCZmnm2BjDAlFD&TARGET |archive-date=2012-10-04 |url-status=dead }}</ref>
